description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces 2". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Galápagos tortoise
-Magnificent frigatebird
-Galápagos sea lion
-Red-footed booby
-Sally lightfoot crab
-Sea turtle
-Galápagos penguin
-Galápagos marine iguana
-Red-footed booby
-Galápagos land iguana
name: Galápagos: Wildlife Sanctuary
